text: daembi khnhom nung sang ampeula champoh avei del khnhom ban baohbng chaol kanlongomk . min dauchnaoh te. pitabrakd nasa vea kreante chea peakyasaamdei delke niyeay tte tebonnaoh . haey now khangmoukh puokke mean chonhcheang( kheang puokke min aoy tralbtow lokey vinh) rhautadl thngai del puokke trauv ke thveu aoy rsa laengvinh
